及後在1970年，校方獲得銀行貸款，購入原址三至五樓作為校舍。日校可以由二十二班增擴展到三十三班，而日夜校的學生數目超過一千人<ref name="重生校友通訊" />。1978年，政府推行[[香港教育|九年免費教育]]政策，以直接分派方式安排學生入讀中一年級。此舉令重生中學日校部在招生方面面臨經濟困難<ref name="重生校友通訊" />。校董會往後於1986年向教育署將辦學團體註冊成非牟利機構「重生教育機構有限公司」<ref name="重生校友通訊" />。而且於1980年代已有計劃申請轉型為一所屋邨津貼中學<ref>{{cite news | title=非牟利私校轉津問題 當局應切實合理解決 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJPwpnLpb9BMH&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=22&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=5 | publisher=大公報 | date=1987-06-15 | accessdate=2021-01-27 | quote= | archive-date=2021-02-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205204955/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJPwpnLpb9BMH&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=22&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | dead-url=no }}</ref>。到了1990年8月應當局推出的直接資助計劃提出轉型申請。最終基於重生中學的校舍不符合條件規定<ref name="重生校友通訊" />，便於1993年8月停辦<ref>{{cite web |url=http://chungsangalumni.org/page57.php |title=重生校友通訊 |last= |first= |date=2016-06-20 |website= |publisher=重生校友會 |access-date=2021-01-27 |quote= |archive-date=2021-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131190148/http://chungsangalumni.org/page57.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由創校到結校，重生中學曾附設小學部、幼稚園部及夜校<ref>{{cite news | title=重生中學日夜校 昨舉行聯歡晚會 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJO6vQZu2l5AH&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=1&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=5 | publisher=大公報 | date=1973-04-16 | accessdate=2021-01-27 | quote= | archive-date=2021-02-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205050106/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJO6vQZu2l5AH&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=1&_coverpag